show.description: Her stepfather abused Shiyononova. To save her mother, she agreed to marry Jiyaan, who is a handsome coma patient. She plans to enjoy Jiyaan's money after his death. But when Jiyaan unexpectedly wakes up on their wedding night, Shiyononova's life changes forever.
